oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Del Reeves and Darrell McCall at Highland County Fairgrounds (21409)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Reeves, Del; McCall, Darrell;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Del Reeves, Darrell McCall and Tennessee Jim at the Highland County Fairgrounds on August 6. Poster features a metal photoplate of Del Reeves. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/23232.
